{"tid":1419732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"記住呢場仗， 註定係贏咗先可以救返曬所有人出嚟","createTime":"2019-08-06T02:26:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T01:38:01.000Z","uid":43785,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"97a2e31b922d5db22422616f5e374dedb5234873","tid":1419732,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:26:35.000Z","msg":"好多人為香港貢獻咗自己嘅前途， 我哋依家係用上香港嘅前途去救番義士嘅前途。<br />\n相反若果呢場仗輸咗嘅話， 香港人一定會被清算， 香港嘅前途同義士嘅前途都冇晒架啦！<br />\n<br />\n記住呢場仗， 由開始嘅一刻已經返唔到轉頭，註定係贏咗先可以救返曬所有人出嚟。<br />\n所有人出唔到嚟， 唔係因為唔得，而係因為我哋未贏。 因為林鄭月娥未答應香港市民五大訴求。<br />\n<br />\n當林鄭月娥同習近平答應我哋五大訴求嘅時候。<br />\n所有義士都可以放返曬出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n記住不要絕望， 更不要放棄希望<br />\n看似好遙遠，但我哋其實只差一步<br />\n「五大訴求， 缺一不可」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人加油！"},{"pid":"4a7cda6ad87bcfb944d857dc05de5d0562cb59d8","tid":1419732,"uid":43785,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:26:56.000Z","msg":"記住呢一個群組活動冇大台， 冇人會走出去認輸。<br />\n<br />\n你除非拉走曬200萬香港人 ，否則我地係注定唔會失敗。我哋只不過係未成功！"},{"pid":"990f2d6cc601f53166e5f624c53260cb8fb891c5","tid":1419732,"uid":51848,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:27:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/949ABR0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F949ABR0.png&h=3703a721&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d4da03618255aa859df2a7e7df622f9b3f9b777e","tid":1419732,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:27:19.000Z","msg":"我哋今日雖然未令林鄭月娥跪低。<br />\n<br />\n但一定會為今後抗爭引起蝴蝶效應， 冇人會諗到陳同佳會搞到咁大單嘢。<br />\n<br />\n更加冇人會諗到元朗嗰單嘢會激起更多人支持我地。<br />\n<br />\n暫時不要散播負面住！<br />\n聽朝仲有輿論戰要打， 集中屌黑社會嗰度。<br />\n中聯辦再搵刀手同黑社會斬人"},{"pid":"e204e49b9db393c14b3bdf1652956b1d8fe7d8bf","tid":1419732,"uid":51848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:27:58.000Z","msg":"鳩硬蛇又想拉手足🤤"},{"pid":"ffbc9b96458f46f9f639d18d4a52f1c0f17ace9f","tid":1419732,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:27:59.000Z","msg":"我地唔可以輸<br />\n輸左一定比支共清算屠城 今日新疆 明日香港呀！"},{"pid":"4bfa6e38606ca148549ed4674de1200ffb31715d","tid":1419732,"uid":34705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:28:24.000Z","msg":"同意，仲有兄弟要救"},{"pid":"994760d2e3849023098133649e92e43a99551e96","tid":1419732,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4bfa6e38606ca148549ed4674de1200ffb31715d","tid":1419732,"uid":34705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:28:24.000Z","msg":"同意，仲有兄弟要救"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:28:37.000Z","msg":"冇錯， 我哋唔可以認輸<br />\n輸咗嘅話，等於輸咗個香港， 輸曬所有位香港抗爭個嘅義士，輸埋我哋下一代生活嘅地方。"},{"pid":"c1e678f978e0769ab2703e07fb8d7f43cf63f107","tid":1419732,"uid":33796,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:29:38.000Z","msg":"鳩蛇又要交數"},{"pid":"81a6fbccba460292d57028b2b3a570582a804594","tid":1419732,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:30:12.000Z","msg":"喂係咪真係冇人識立法會議員呀，輪流又好整個3點鍾毛姨又好，最基本都要日日開記招recap當日警暴同指出政府記招點樣不盡不實"},{"pid":"cd3bbb7392e8883471a11ac25333f6448d3887e8","tid":1419732,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e204e49b9db393c14b3bdf1652956b1