<br />\n2. 有冷氣<br />\n3. 已經有巴絲係度<br />\n4. 已經罷緊工<br />\n5. 林鄭好驚提機場<br />\n6. 機場cancel已上國際頭版<br />\n7. 機場特警係速龍，要佢地分飾兩角，姐係壯士斷臂<br />\n8. 唔會係室內開槍、放Tear Gas<br />\n9. 如果黑警封路 = 助攻<br />\n10. 最佳國際文宣機會"},{"pid":"29a3a26ac7fad58c01058f4471f16b42a7216f8b","tid":1419732,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45c54550b2f927cdea6ec618cbd9d91313169f16","tid":1419732,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:50:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>機場呀</strong></span><br />\n1. 香港旅遊業春袋<br />\n2. 有冷氣<br />\n3. 已經有巴絲係度<br />\n4. 已經罷緊工<br />\n5. 林鄭好驚提機場<br />\n6. 機場cancel已上國際頭版<br />\n7. 機場特警係速龍，要佢地分飾兩角，姐係壯士斷臂<br />\n8. 唔會係室內開槍、放Tear Gas<br />\n9. 如果黑警封路 = 助攻<br />\n10. 最佳國際文宣機會"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:14:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e3b7e3224c6bab0fbbea807650b76a7a57232fa7","tid":1419732,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:36:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fe259f01fb6553a1155f3bf2d1c0e1174f8d7a8","tid":1419732,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:53:46.000Z","msg":"放番所有人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04f41f45df44e293fa39a83c57f5bcdd229cc820","tid":1419732,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:02:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fda969930c7635bf881c94efb40607aeab42779b","tid":1419732,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:48:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b3403fde3eedf7ab06b9dccc99234e16bc069a7","tid":1419732,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:53:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"435cdd605